      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry which shares impeller diameter range, volute topology, and operating flow-speed envelope with the subject CPB device. Porcine blood used in validation experiments is accepted surrogate for human blood in hemolysis studies per ISO 10993-4. Validation domain adequately covers COU operating space."
